VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'absorb it, blue wavelengths reflect back more strongly. &gt;&gt; So, you can see that they\'re discussing the concept of blue eyes, and we get this wonderful zoom into the eye, and then explanations with annotations. Now, we get these transitions between the different shots'

